  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Kadirgamam flag hoisting tonight",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The annual flag hoisting event of the historic Kathirgamam Kandan Temple will be held today (29) Friday evening.",
        "On the other hand, the flag hoisting ceremony of the Udavai Hill Sri Murugan Temple will be held today under the leadership of the Gurus of the Temple Pradham Guru Shivsiri K.K. Seetharam.",
        "15 consecutive days of festivals starting with flag hoisting, berahara will be held, the tirtha utsavam will be held at Kathirgam on 12th, similarly, the tirtha utsavam of Udgai Murugan Temple will be held on 11th.",
        "It is reported that devotees traveling on the forest path to Kathirgamat are suffering from continuous rain.",
        "It is noteworthy that around 9,000 Padayatra pilgrims, including the group that left from Selvach Sannidhi Temple, Jaffna, have reached Kathirgam so far."
      ],
